ne%20of%20that%20was%20really%20serious%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%2C%20not%20if%20he's%20serious%20about%20Trump.%20A%20lot%20of%20rich%20and%20powerful%20people%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fharold-hamm-this-election-is-oil-industrys-most-important-ever-1033683642%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elike%20the%20billionaire%20oilman%20Harold%20Hamm%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20are%20clear%20about%20why%20they%20support%20Trump.%20He%20is%20for%20them%2C%20so%20they%20are%20for%20him.%20Now%20we%20know%20Musk%20isn't%20any%20different.%20Maybe%20he%20never%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStupid%20Soros%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk's%20attempts%20to%20wrangle%20Trump%20for%20his%20personal%20gains%20are%20not%20the%20only%20ways%20that%20he%20is%20jumping%20into%20electoral%20politics.%20Based%20on%20the%20early%20returns%20for%20these%20other%20efforts%2C%20he%20appears%20no%20more%20successful%20at%20influencing%20the%20microscale%20of%20politics%20than%20he%20is%20at%20working%20the%20hallowed%20halls%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusk's%20endeavor%20to%20start%20a%20super%20PAC%20%E2%80%94%20a%20slush%20fund%20for%20political%20activism%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20a%20flop%2C%20according%20to%20recent%20reporting%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2Finside-elon-musks-hands-on-push-to-win-800-000-voters-for-trump-0a7d55b3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20stated%20goal%20of%20the%20PAC%20is%20to%20register%20some%20800%2C000%20new%20voters%2C%20who%20would%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20boost%20Trump.%20Musk%20tapped%20his%20fellow%20Silicon%20Valley%20entrepreneur%20Joe%20Lonsdale%20in%20April%20to%20start%20raising%20money.%20Lonsdale's%20pitch%20to%20prospective%20donors%20was%20that%20if