%3A1723715309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112545453%2Cimgsize-725627.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhad-higher-hopes-for-you-swati-maliwal-writes-to-mamata-banerjee-over-kolkata-rape-and-murder-case%2Farticleshow%2F112545369.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhad-higher-hopes-for-you-swati-maliwal-writes-to-mamata-banerjee-over-kolkata-rape-and-murder-case%2Farticleshow%2F112545369.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20Arrested%20For%20Violence%20At%20Kolkata%20Hospital%20Where%20Doctor%20Was%20Raped-Murdered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENine%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20after%20a%20mob%20vandalised%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Thursday%20during%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20institution%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20had%20organised%20a%20vigil%2C%20calling%20it%20'women%2C%20reclaim%20the%20night'%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20During%20the%20vigil%2C%20which%20began%20around%2011%20pm%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20some%20people%20entered%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20went%20on%20a%20rampage.%20Vehicles%20were%20attacked%2C%20public%20property%20was%20damaged%20and%20the%20police%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20a%20lathicharge%20as%20well%20as%20firing%20teargas%20shells%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%20The%20Kolkata%20Police%20said%2015%20policemen%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20police%20released%20some%20photos%20of%20people%20believed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20mob%20that%20vandalised%20the%20hospital%20and%20sought%20information%20about%20them.%20The%20photos%20were%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20and%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20suspected%20rioters%20were%20circled.%20The%20arrests%20were%20announced%20hours%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20nine%20arrested%20people%20have%20not%20been%20revealed%2C%20a%20doctor%2C%20Anubhav%20Mondal%2C%20who%20is%20participating%20in%20the%20protests%20outside%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20said%20he%20was%20among%20those%20circled%20in%20the%20photographs%20circulated%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20protests%20will%20continue%20and%20get%20bigger.%20Whoever%20thinks%20they%20can%20instil%20fear%20in%20us%20will%20not%20succeed%2C%20we%20want%20justice%20at%20any%20cost.%20Our%20most%20important%20demand%20is%20a%20neutral%20investigation%20through%20a%20court-monitored%20process%2C%20and%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mondal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20claims%20were%20made%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20seminar%20hall%20where%20the%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20was%20also%20vandalised%20by%20the%20mob%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20said%20nothing%20of%20the%20sort%20had%20happened%20and%20warned%20people%20against%20spreading%20rumours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrime%20scene%20is%20Seminar%20Room%20and%20it%20has%20not%20been%20touched.%20Don't%20spread%20unverified%20news.%20We%20will%20initiate%20legal%20action%20for%20spreading%20rumours%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernor%20Visit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20also%20visited%20the%20hospital%20on%20Thursday%20and%20assured%20doctors%20and%20medical%20students%20that%20he%20was%20standing%20with%20them%20after%20they%20told%20him%20that%20they%20were%20feeling%20insecure%20after%20the%20killing%20and%20violence%2C%20and%20were%20feeling%20%26quot%3Btraumatised%20and%20terrorised%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20with%20you.%20We%20will%20fight%20it%20out%20and%20not%20allow%20these%20ghastly%20things.%20We%20will%20take%20positive%20action%20which%20will%20be%20exemplary%20for%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20told%20the%20doctors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProbe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBI%20team%2C%20which%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20has%20met%20the%20family%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trainee%20doctor's%20body%20was%20found%20last%20Friday%20and%20an%20autopsy%20report%2C%20which%20had%20put%20the%20time%20of%20death%20between%203%20and%205%20am%2C%20revealed%20that%20several%20injuries%20were%20inflicted%20on%20her%20before%20she%20was%20smothered%20to%20death.%20The%20police%20had%20arrested%20a%20civic%20volunteer%2C%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20the%20CBI's%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20have%20told%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20that%20150%20mg%20of%20semen%20was%20found%20in%20her%20body%2C%20indicating%20that%20she%20was%20gang-raped.%20%26quot%3BNo%20step%20taken%20to%20arrest%20any%20other%20offenders%20while%20the%20evidence%20clearly%20indicates%20that%20their%20daughter%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20gang%20rape%20and%20murder%2C%20a%20crime%20that%20could%20not%20have%20been%20committed%20by%20one%20person%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20parents'%20petition%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723715280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvk1aso28_kolkata-protest_625x300_15_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F9-arrested-for-violence-at-kolkata-hospital-where-doctor-was-raped-murdered-6343135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nine%20people%20have%20be