get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasing%20isolation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20intimate%20relationship%20can%20be%20especially%20valuable.%20And%2C%20pragmatically%2C%20finding%20a%20partner%20can%20have%20some%20economic%20advantages%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20things%20are%20cheaper%20when%20they're%20divided%20by%20two.%20But%20the%20price%20tag%20to%20find%20the%20right%20person%20is%20getting%20higher.%20Love%2C%20in%20this%20economy%2C%20is%20increasingly%20reserved%20only%20for%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBring%20in%20the%20dating%20coaches!%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20magical%20financial%20formula%20for%20a%20relationship%20(sadly)%2C%20but%20to%20sketch%20out%20the%20new%20cost%20of%20love%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20ask%20several%20dating%20coaches%20a%20few%20questions%20that%20could%20help%20me%20develop%20a%20relationship%20road%20map%3A%20How%20long%20does%20it%20usually%20take%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20you're%20compatible%3F%20How%20much%20should%20a%20date%20cost%3F%20Who%20is%20expected%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20tab%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FJ2eFR%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20roadmap%20for%20dating%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coaches%20said%20it%20usually%20takes%20about%20three%20months%20of%20seeing%20someone%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20week%20for%20most%20people%20to%20consider%20it%20a%20relationship.%20So%20that's%20at%20least%2012%20dates%20before%20getting%20into%20a%20relationship.%20Not%20every%20date%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20costs%20and%20activities%20will%20vary%20by%20person%2C%20location%2C%20and%20what%20you're%20drawn%20to.%20Amy%20Nobile%20Messing%2C%20a%20New%20York%20City%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flove-amy-nyc-matchmaker-perfect-dating-profile-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20holistic%20and%20technology-based%20approach%20and%20clients%20aged%2025%20to%2081%2C%20recommended%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini%20screener%20date%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20first%20meetup%20before%20escalating%20to%20anything%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20dates%20should%20not%20be%20the%20traditional%20go%20out%20to%20dinner%20for%20four%20hours%20and%20spend%20a%20ton%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20really%20shouldn't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDamona%20Hoffman%2C%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20dating%20coach%2C%20similarly%20recommended%20doing%20drinks%20because%20clients%20could%20otherwise%20end%20up%20overstaying%20their%20welcome%20and%20shelling%20out%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20dates%20should%20be%20something%20short%20and%20sweet%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20date%20is%20when%20the%20tabs%20get%20more%20substantial%20%E2%80%94%20a%20longer%20meal%20where%20you%20can%20sit%20across%20from%20one%20another%20and%20delve%20deeper.%20Daphney%20Poyser%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fernconnections.com%2Fpress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFern%20Connections%3C%2Fa%3E%20specializes%20in%20queer%20dating%2C%20recommended%20dinner%20and%20an%20activity%20like%20mini%20golf%2C%20ax%20throwing%2C%20or%20cooking%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20things%20progress%2C%20another%20big%20question%20is%20who's%20picking%20up%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decision%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20host%20of%20gendered%20assumptions%20and%20changing%20norms.%20Messing%20said%20that%20among%20her%20heterosexual%20clients%2C%20there's%20still%20an%20expectation%20that%20the%20man%20is%20paying%20for%20all%20the%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20in%20a%20heterosexual%20relationship%20and%20you%20believe%20in%20chivalry%2C%20which%2C%20again%2C%2095%25%20of%20my%20clients%20do%2C%20then%20the%20man%20is%20paying%2C%20period%2C%20end%20of%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Messing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20answer%20is%20not%20as%20clear-cut%20for%20same-sex%20couples%2C%20couples%20who%20don't%20skew%20toward%20traditional%20heterosexual%20norms%2C%20or%20younger%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20younger%20daters%2C%20they're%20like%2C%20'Of%20course%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20split%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20date%2C'%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20huge%20shift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoyser%20tells%20her%20clients%20that%20everybody%20should%20expect%20to%20split%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20like%20someone%20and%20they%20like%20you%2C%20then%20you%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20split%20the%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20Poyser%20said.%20Among%20Messing's%20queer%20clients%2C%20the%20rule%20of%20thumb%20has%20been%20that%20whoever%20asked%20the%20other%20person%20out%20or%20planned%20the%20date%20should%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20naturally%20trade-off%20as%20things%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20for%20simplicity's%20sake%2C%20in%20our%20road%20map%2C%20let's%20assume%20that%20you're%20always%20splitting%20costs%2C%20with%20the%20expectation%20that%20straight%20men%20will%20pick%20up%20the%20bill%20more%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20nitty-gritty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20time%2C%20shape%20of%20the%20activities%2C%20and%20share%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20we%20can%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20dating%20costs%20look%20like%20for%20a%2012-date%20plan.%20Of%20course%2C%20these%20numbers%20are%20all%20approximations%20%E2%80%94%20your%20favorite%20restaurant%20or%20activity%20might%20cost%20more%20or%20less.%20But%20to%20get%20to%20rough%20estimates%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20stick%20close%20to%20real%20menu%20prices%20and%20approximate%20how%20much%20costs%20have%20risen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FOzllu%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22How%20much%20a%20relationship%20roughly%20costs%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20coaches'%20first-date%20suggestions%20generally%20boiled%20down%20to%20drinks%2C%20I%20started%20the%20tabulation%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20cocktail%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconormclaughlin.net%2F2019%2F06%2Fa-semi-scientific-study-of-american-cocktail-prices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20%2412%20in%202019%20across%20major%20US%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Adjust%20that%20for%20inflation%2C%20and%20it's%20about%20%2414.50%20in%202024%20dollars.%20For%20alcohol-free%20drinkers%2C%20the%20average%20price%20of%20a%20coffee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fny.eater.com%2F2024%2F5%2F9%2F24151420%2Fprice-of-coffee-nyc-latte-cold-brew%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20about%20%246%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F02%2F03%2Fpeople-in-this-city-spend-the-most-on-coffeeits-not-new-york-or-la.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomparable%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20other%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20everything%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20movies%2C%20prices%20vary%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20average%20ticket%20cost%20%2411.75%20in%202022%2C%20the%20research%20firm%20EntTelligence%20estimated%3B%20round%20up%20for%20recent%20inflation%2C%20and%20the%20average%20movie%20ticket%20costs%20about%20%2412%2C%20plus%20%2427%20for%20a%20large%20popcorn%2C%20a%20drink%2C%20and%20candy.%20The%20same%20logic%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20museums%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F01%2Farts%2Fdesign%2Fmuseums-raise-admission-fees-guggenheim.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETicket%20prices%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20ticked%20up%20to%20the%20%2430%20range.%20I%20chose%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20as%20our%20museum%20date%20spot%20because%20it%20is%2C%20inarguably%2C%20a%20great%20place%20to%20go%20on%20a%20date.%20The%20cost%20of%20an%20adult%20ticket%3A%20%2428%20for%20non-NYC%20residents.%20I%20also%20chose%20a%20premium%20concert%20experience%20for%20our%20daters%20since%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjennifer-lopez-cancels-tour-slow-ticket-sales-concerts-prices-ticketmaster-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20less%20likely%20to%20get%20canceled%20than%20smaller%20shows%20right%20now%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Pollstar%2C%20a%20live-music%20industry%20publication%2C%20found%20that%20the%20average%20ticket%20price%20for%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20top%20100%20performing%20artists%20was%20%24123.25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20up%20from%20%2495.63%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumbers%20got%20a%20little%20fuzzier%20when%20I%20looked%20at%20how%20much%20it%20cost%20to%20go%20out%20to%20dinner%20or%20order%20in.%20I%20chose%20my%20favorite%20date%20spot%20%E2%80%94%20Thai72%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20menu%20example%2C%20and%20it%20tracked%20fairly%20closely%20with%20MoneyGeek's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneygeek.com%2Fliving%2Fanalysis%2Fcost-of-a-date-in-major-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimate%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20romantic%20dinner%20out%20costs%20%2496.%20Similarly%2C%20I%20used%20my%20favorite%20pizza%20spot%20%E2%80%94%20Mama's%20Too%20%E2%80%94%20to%20gauge%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20nicer%20takeout%20pizza%20and%20then%20added%20a%20Trader%20Joe's%20Caesar%20salad%20and%20a%20bottle%20of%20Josh%20ros%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20have%20a%20few%20dates%20under%20their%20belt%2C%20I%20figured%20that%20many%20daters%20clustered%20in%20too-small%20urban%20apartments%20would%20want%20to%20get%20some%20breathing%20room.%20After%20all%2C%20there's%20nothing%20like%20a%20day%20trip%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20longer-term%20travel%20with%20your%20partner%20might%20look%20like.%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20driving%20from%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Hudson%2C%20New%20York%2C%20a%20popular%20mini-road-trip%20destination%20(and%2C%20conveniently%2C%20a%20great%20way%20to%20visit%20Business%20Insider's%20economic-data%20editor%2C%20Andy%20Kiersz%2C%20who%20helped%20oversee%20these%20calculations).%20For%20our%20later%20dates%2C%20I%20also%20included%20a%20few%20spicier%20ideas%2C%20like%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20board-game%20caf%C3%A9%20Hex%26amp%3BCo.%2C%20a%20pasta-making%20class%2C%20and%20a%20cheese%20tasting%20at%20Murray's%20Cheese%2C%20as%20fancier%20date%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20these%20estimates%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20how%20dating%20adds%20up%3A%20Our%20hypothetical%20dater%20is%20spending%20%24650%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%2012-date%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estimates%20also%20don't%20take%20into%20account%20the%20subtler%20costs%20of%20dating.%20That%20could%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20the%20price%20of%20the%20commute%20to%20and%20from%20your%20meetup%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20cost%20you%20%245.80%20if%20you%20took%20New%20York%20City's%20subway%20%E2%80%94%20or%20having%20to%20fill%20up%20your%20gas%20tank.%20The%20dating%20experts%20I%20spoke%20with%20also%20listed%20services%20their%20clients%20may%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20for%20dating%2C%20from%20hair%20and%20makeup%20to%20Botox%20and%20dating-app%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20said%20that%20beauty%20norms%20had%20shifted%3A%20Skincare%20and%20different%20types%20of%20fillerl%2C%20along%20with%20Botox%2C%20are%20increasingly%20seen%20as%20necessary%20parts%20of%20a%20beauty%20regimen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20beauty%20enhancements%2C%20people%20aren't%20really%20thinking%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20them%2C%20but%20many%20times%20the%20reason%20that%20they're%20doing%20it%20is%20for%20attraction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20consider%20that%20a%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20costs%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20incorporate%20a%20few%20of%20the%20major%20categories%20into%20the%20road%20map.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyouprobablyneedahaircut.com%2Fhow-much-does-a-haircut-cost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einformal%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20salons%20across%20the%20country%20pegged%20the%20average%20haircut%20at%20%2456%2C%20so%20add%20one%20of%20those%20to%20the%20tab%20for%20the%20three-month%20getting-you-know-you%20period.%20In%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20the%20data-analytics%20firm%20Inmar%20Intelligence%2C%20one-third%20of%20surveyed%20consumers%20said%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeauty-shoppers-still-spending-big-as-us-consumers-cut-elsewhere-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espent%20over%20%24500%20on%20beauty%20products%20in%20the%20past%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20that%20works%20out%20to%20%24125%20in%20beauty-product%20spending%2C%20if%20we're%20accounting%20for%20around%20a%20three-month%20period.%20Meanwhile%2C%20an%20informal%202022%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.styleseat.com%2Fblog%2Fwaxing-cost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20full%20body%20wax%20was%20%24152%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com%2Fstyle-beauty%2Fbeauty%2Fa36462846%2Fbotox-cost-guide%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECosmopolitan%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20that%20low-end%20forehead%20Botox%20would%20cost%20you%20%24300.%20Taken%20together%2C%20that%20could%20mean%20up%20to%20%24500%20more%20in%20beauty%20spending%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModern%20dating%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20new%20cost%3A%20forking%20over%20money%20for%20dating%20apps.%20In%20a%202022%20Pew%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Finternet%2F2023%2F02%2F02%2Fthe-who-where-and-why-of-online-dating-in-the-u-s%2F%3Futm_source%3Dnpr_newsletter%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_content%3D20240202%26utm_term%3D9250242%26utm_campaign%3Dmoney%26utm_id%3D8562679%26orgid%3D128%26utm_att1%3D%23paid-to-use-a-dating-site-or-app%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoll%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20adults%20who%20were%20online%20dating%2C%2035%25%20said%20that%20they'd%20paid%20to%20use%20one.%20Messing%20recommended%20paying%20for%20HingeX%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F90849674%2Fhinge-is-rolling-out-its-50-per-month-subscription-on-thursday%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2450%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbumble.com%2Fen-us%2Fthe-buzz%2Fbumble-premium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBumble%20Premium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20runs%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Freview%2Fbumble-premium-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2440%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hoffman%20doesn't%20have%20a%20uniform%20recommendation%20for%20dating%20apps%20but%20said%20people%20should%20pay%20for%20what's%20important%20to%20them.%20Similarly%2C%20Poyser%20recommended%20paying%20for%20Hinge%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20average%20dater%20that%20only%20started%20using%20dating%20apps%20in%20the%20last%20five%20or%2010%20years%20has%20what%20I%20feel%20like%20is%20an%20unrealistic%20expectation%20of%20what%20they%20should%20get%20from%20a%20free%20dating-app%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20She%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20apps%20are%20breaking%20out%20the%20different%20levels%20of%20service%2C%20different%20features%20that%20you%20can%20pay%20for%2C%20and%20it's%20kind%20of%20like%20streaming%20television.%20You%20just%20pay%20for%20the%20ones%20that%20you%20are%20going%20to%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20also%20choose%20to%20employ%20a%20dating%20coach.%20Messing's%20services%20run%20%2425%2C000%20for%20a%20four-month%20program.%20Hoffman's%20costs%20range%20from%20%249%20into%20the%20five%20figures%3B%20she%20said%20her%20most%20popular%20program%20was%20group%20coaching%2C%20which%20costs%20%242%2C500.%20Poyser%20said%20that%20she%20charged%20%24200%20for%20her%20initial%20one-hour%20session%20and%20then%20%24150%20for%20bundled%20sessions%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20adding%20up%20all%20the%20direct%20and%20implicit%20costs%20of%20dating%2C%20the%20price%20of%20finding%20that%20special%20someone%20rang%20in%20at%20about%20%241%2C000%20for%20around%2012%20dates.%20Adjusting%20for%20inflation%2C%20that%20would've%20come%20out%20to%20about%20%24800%20in%202019%20%E2%80%94%20without%20accounting%20for%20the%20loneliness%20and%20geographical%20shifts%20the%20pandemic%20caused%2C%20where%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20spend%20more%20to%20find%20friends.%20Notably%2C%20the%20%2450%20paid%20version%20of%20Hinge%20that%20our%20coaches%20recommended%20rolled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F90849674%2Fhinge-is-rolling-out-its-50-per-month-subscription-on-thursday%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eout%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2023%2F09%2F22%2Ftinder-500-a-month-subscription%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epricier%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.platformer.news%2Fgrindr-ai-boyfriend-wingman-monetization-paid-taps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofferings%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20more%20recent%20invention%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20just%20the%20cost%20to%20get%20into%20a%20relationship.%20Even%20deeper%20down%20the%20romantic%20path%2C%20couples%20face%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faverage-wedding-cost-in-biggest-metro-areas-of-us-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20soaring%20cost%20of%20weddings%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-gen-z-parents-struggle-lonely-childcare-costs-money-friends-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20price%20of%20being%20a%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20does%20that%20mean%20for%20all%20of%20us%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20daters%20out%20there%20might%20not%20be%20too%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20getting%20into%20a%20relationship%20is%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20though%20even%20I%20was%20taken%20aback%20by%20just%20how%20much%20I'd%20been%20sinking%20into%20finding%20a%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20rising%20costs%20of%20dating%20aren't%20just%20an%20issue%20for%20the%20lonely%20hearts%20of%20America%2C%20they%20also%20point%20to%20a%20growing%20problem%20for%20everyone%20in%20the%20US%3A%20The%20things%20that%20bring%20us%20joy%2C%20happiness%2C%20or%20meaning%20are%20all%20getting%20more%20expensive.%20Dinner%20out%20with%20friends%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-prices-cheapest-option-groceries-restaurants-fast-food-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Going%20on%20vacation%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-people-booking-vacations-despite-finances-debt-summer-economy-travel-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20pricier%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Owning%20a%20pet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotect-finances-pets-likely-recession-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20cost%20you%20more%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20those%20who%20have%20moved%20beyond%20the%20cycle%20of%20dating%20and%20into%20building%20a%20family%20are%20facing%20these%20price%20pressures.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%