%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112544395.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanbir%20Kapoor%20and%20Alia%20Bhatt%20were%20spotted%20in%20the%20city%20with%20Raha%20and%20netizens%20couldn't%20stop%20gushing%20over%20the%20adorable%20little%20girl%20again%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20wearing%20saffron%20on%20Independence%20Day!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoor-and-alia-bhatts-baby-girl-raha-soaks-into-the-independence-day-spirit-as-she-wears-a-saffron-dress-and-looks-adorable-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F112544395.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOnly%20Single-Line%20Order...%26quot%3B%3A%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20Lawyer%20Reacts%20To%20CAS%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association's%20(IOA)%20advocate%20Vidushpat%20Singhania%20confirmed%20that%20only%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle-line%20order%20has%20come%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20a%20detailed%20order.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20CAS%20released%20a%20statement%20to%20confirm%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20application%20field%20by%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20on%20August%207%20has%20been%20dismissed.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20Vidushpat%20said%20that%20the%20CAS%20has%20not%20cited%20a%20reason%20why%20has%20it%20been%20dismissed%20her%20appeal.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20CAS's%20decision%20can%20be%20appealed%20against%20at%20the%20Swiss%20Federal%20Tribunal%20within%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20detailed%20order%20has%20come%20yet.%20Only%20a%20single-line%20order%20has%20come%20so%20far%20that%20her%20appeal%20has%20been%20dismissed.%20They%20have%20not%20cited%20a%20reason%20why%20has%20it%20been%20dismissed%20or%20why%20did%20they%20take%20so%20much%20time...We%20were%20both%20surprised%20and%20disappointed%20that%20a%20decision%20came%20last%20evening%20and%20her%20appeal%20was%20dismissed...%20We%20hope%20that%20the%20detailed%20order%20will%20come%20in%2010-15%20days...%20CAS%20decision%20can%20be%20appealed%20against%20at%20the%20Swiss%20Federal%20Tribunal%20within%2030%20days.%20The%2030-day%20time%20will%20begin%20after%20a%20detailed%20order%20comes.%20Harish%20Salve%20is%20with%20us%2C%20he%20will%20guide%20us.%20We%20will%20sit%20with%20him%2C%20draft%20an%20appeal%20and%20file%20it...%2C%26quot%3B%20Vidushpat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%2C%20the%20verdict%20was%20originally%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2013%20at%209%3A30%20pm%20IST%2C%20but%20was%20delayed%20to%20August%2016.%20However%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20announced%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20was%20set%20to%20face%20Sarah%20Ann%20Hildebrandt%20of%20the%20United%20States%20for%20the%20gold%20medal%20on%20August%207.%20She%20was%20disqualified%20before%20the%20women's%2050kg%20final%20after%20exceeding%20the%2050kg%20weight%20limit%20before%20the%20final%20on%20August%207.%20During%20the%20weigh-in%2C%20she%20was%20found%20to%20be%20100%20grams%20over%20the%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20disqualification%2C%20Vinesh%20appealed%20to%20award%20her%20the%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%2050kg%20weight%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%208%2C%20Vinesh%20penned%20an%20emotional%20to%20announce%20her%20decision%20to%20retire%20from%20wrestling.%20%26quot%3BMaa%20kushti%20(wrestling)%20won%20against%20me%2C%20I%20lost.%20Forgive%20me%2C%20your%20dream%20and%20my%20courage%20have%20been%20broken.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20more%20strength%20now.%20Goodbye%20Wrestling%202001-2024.%20I%20will%20always%20be%20indebted%20to%20you%20all%20for%20forgiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Phogat%20said%20in%20her%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHildebrandt%20secured%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20women's%2050kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20aft