%20reason%20a%20man%20cannot%20sue%20after%20his%20wife%20suffered%20an%20allergic%20reaction%20and%20died%20after%20eating%20at%20Disney%20World%20resort%20in%20Florida%2C%20the%20company's%20lawyers%20have%20argued.%20Disney%20said%20the%20man%20signed%20away%20his%20right%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20company%20when%20he%20agreed%20to%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20Disney%2B%20during%20a%20free%20trial%20of%20the%20streaming%20service%20several%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20Piccolo%20filed%20a%20%26quot%3Bwrongful%20death%26quot%3B%20lawsuit%20against%20Disney%20after%20his%20wife%20Kanokporn%20Tangsuan%2C%20a%20doctor%20from%20New%20York%2C%20died%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Piccolo%20has%20claimed%20in%20his%20lawsuit%20that%20his%20wife%20died%20after%20suffering%20an%20allergic%20reaction%20from%20her%20meal%20at%20a%20resort%20restaurant%20in%20Disney%20Springs%20at%20the%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20Resort%20in%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Piccolo%20said%20his%20wife%20had%20a%20severe%20allergy%20to%20dairy%20and%20nuts%20and%20the%20couple%20questioned%20the%20restaurant%20waiter%20numerous%20times%20about%20the%20ingredients%20of%20the%20meal%20they%20ordered.%20He%20said%20they%20were%20reassured%20that%20their%20food%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ballergen%20free%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20their%20meal%2C%20he%20claimed%20his%20wife%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20acute%20allergic%20reaction%26quot%3B%20and%20died%20later%20that%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20autopsy%2C%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20death%20was%20determined%20as%20anaphylaxis%20--%20a%20flood%20of%20chemicals%20that%20can%20cause%20the%20body%20to%20go%20into%20shock%20--%20due%20to%20high%20levels%20of%20dairy%20and%20nuts%20in%20her%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20lawsuit%20against%20Walt%20Disney%20Parks%20and%20Resorts%2C%20he%20argued%20that%20the%20waiter%20was%20negligent%20and%20demanded%20damages%20over%20%2450%2C000.%3C