%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20we%20have%20increased%20medical%20seats%20to%20nearly%20one%20lakh.%20(But)%20today%2C%20around%2025%2C000%20youths%20go%20abroad%20every%20year%20for%20medical%20education.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%2075%2C000%20new%20seats%20will%20be%20created%20in%20the%20medical%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Health%20Ministry%2C%20the%20number%20of%20medical%20colleges%20in%20the%20country%20has%20increased%20by%2088%20per%20cent%20from%202014%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power.%20There%20were%20387%20before%202014%20and%20this%20has%20since%20increased%20to%20731%2C%20the%20government%20said%2C%20adding%20there%20were%20also%20an%20increase%20of%20133%20per%20cent%20seats%20for%20postgraduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20from%20around%2031%2C000%20in%202014%20to%20over%2072%2C000%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20said%20his%20government%20would%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20hospitals%20and%20health%20infrastructure%3B%20in%20June%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20country's%20health%20budget%20had%20been%20increased%20from%20Rs%2079%2C221%20crore%20last%20year%20to%20over%20Rs%2090%2C000%20crore%20for%202024%2F25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20college%20seats%20have%20been%20in%20sharp%20focus%20over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20and%20months%20after%20controversy%20over%20the%20conduct%20and%20results%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20a%20qualifying%20test%20for%20admission%20to%20undergraduate%20courses%20for%20future%20doctors.%20The%20controversy%20broke%20in%20June%20after%20red%20flags%20over%20the%20number%20-%2067%20-%20of%20perfect%20scores%20and%20the%20award%20of%20'grace%20marks'%20to%201%2C563%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20emerged%20that%20the%20question%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20at%20some%20centres%20in%20Patna%20and%20Hazaribagh%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20prompting%20multiple%20appeals%20to%20be%20filed%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20also%20been%20tasked%20with%20investigating%20a%20national%20racket%20of%20leaking%20question%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-will-be-no-neet-re-exam-rules-supreme-court-6170722%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo%20NEET%20Re-Exam%2C%20%26quot%3BCan't%20Conclude%20Sanctity%20Breached%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20however%2C%20the%20top%20court%20ruled%20out%20a%20complete%20re-test%20for%20the%202024%20NEET-UG%20exam%2C%20reasoning%20there%20is%20no%20data%20to%20suggest%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20breach%26quot%3B%20or%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bsanctity%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20examination%2C%20following%20two%20localised%20leaks%20of%20the%20question%20paper%2C%20had%20been%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2023.3%20lakh%20students%20sat%20for%20the%20May%205%20NEET-UG%20exam%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20the%20central%20body%20that%20conducts%20such%20examinations.%20Only%20a%20small%20number%20of%20these%20candidates%20will%20be%20selected%20to%20fill%20the%20limited%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20making%20this%20a%20competitive%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControversy%20over%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20triggered%20a%20massive%20political%20row%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20opposition%2C%20with%20fierce%20squabbles%20inside%20and%20outside%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723701720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ft1nserho_pm-modi_625x300_15_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-independence-day-speech-75-000-new-seats-in-medical-colleges-pms-promise-for-aspiring-doctors-6342080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%2