sday%20as%20he%20delivered%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%20to%20the%20nation%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20Delhi's%20Red%20Fort.%20Declaring%20them%20%26quot%3Bfull%20of%20negativity%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20%26quot%3Bsome%20people%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20India%20grow%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20a%20few%20people%20with%20a%20negative%20mindset%20(are)%20conspiring%20to%20create%20imbalance%20in%20country.%20Nepotism%20and%20casteism%20are%20harming%20society...%20we%20have%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20these%20from%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20comments%20seen%20as%20jabs%20against%20fierce%20rivals%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20and%20his%20BJP%20frequently%20attack%20the%20%26quot%3Bdynastic%20politics%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20'first%20family'%20-%20the%20Gandhis%20-%20accusing%20the%20party%20and%20the%20family%20of%20not%20having%20the%20country's%20interest%20at%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20today%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20spectre%20of%20corruption%2C%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20create%20fear%20in%20minds%20of%20the%20corrupt%20to%20stop%20the%20tradition%20of%20looting%20the%20common%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20after%20the%20BJP%20secured%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20seats%20won%20by%20allies%20after%20the%20party%20itself%20fell%2032%20seats%20short%20of%20majority%20-%20the%20PM%20vowed%20to%20continue%20his%20crackdown%20on%20corruption%2C%20saying%20federal%20agencies%20had%20been%20given%20%26quot%3Bfull%20freedom%26quot%3B%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20sharp%20attack%20comes%20after%20a%20tumultuous%20first%20Parliament%20session%20of%20his%20third%20term%2C%20in%20which%20there%20were%20clashes%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%2C%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20and%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20the%20disqualification%20of%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20The%20political%20crisis%20in%20Bangladesh%20also%20led%20to%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20clash%2C%20though%2C%20was%20over%20the%20Union%20Budget%20presented%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20parts%20of%20which%20the%20Congress%20slammed%20as%20having%20been%20copied%20from%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20controversy%20over%20what%20the%20opposition%20said%20was%20lack%20of%20funds%20for%20states%20not%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%20or%20allies.%20The%20opposition%20pointed%20to%20financial%20packages%20for%20Bihar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20are%20ruled%20by%20key%20BJP%20allies%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20to%20back%20their%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20however%2C%20rubbished%20these%20allegations%2C%20insisting%20that%20all%20states%20received%20due%20attention.%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20in%20her%20reply%20in%20Parliament%2C%20also%20directed%20attention%20to%20budget%20speeches%20made%20by%20earlier%20governments%2C%20specifically%20those%20led%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20picking%20up%20on%20Budgets%20since%202004-5.%20In%202004-5%2C%2017%20states%20were%20not%20named%20in%20the%20budget%20speech.%2016%20states%20not%20named%20in%202006-07...%20In%202009%2C%2026%20states%20were%20not%20named%20--%20Bihar%20and%20UP%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20ask%20the%20UPA%20government%20--%20did%20money%20not%20go%20to%20those%20states%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723694520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1bin9clo_pm-modi-_625x300_15_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-independence-