ampus%20on%20which%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20that%20the%20youngsters%20of%20my%20country%20are%20compelled%20to%20go%20abroad%20to%20study.%20Middle%20class%20families%20have%20to%20spend%20lakhs%20and%20crores%20on%20their%20children's%20education%20overseas.%20We%20want%20to%20develop%20an%20education%20system%20here%20so%20that%20the%20youth%20of%20my%20country%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20abroad%2C%20Instead%2C%20people%20from%20abroad%20come%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20from%20ramparts%20of%20Red%20Fort%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20revived%20Nalanda%20University%20in%20Bihar%20and%20it%20has%20started%20functioning%20now%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20revive%20the%20centuries-old%20Nalanda%20spirit%20in%20the%20education%20sphere%2C%20and%20use%20it%20to%20give%20direction%20to%20global%20knowledge%20traditions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20new%20education%20policy%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20focused%20on%20vernacular%20languages.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20state%20governments%20and%20all%20institutions%20that%20our%20country's%20talent%20must%20not%20face%20a%20language%20barrier.%20We%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20place%20of%20mother%20tongues%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20education%20and%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20has%20implemented%20wide-ranging%20reforms%20not%20to%20satisfy%20experts%20or%20intellectual%20debate%20clubs%2C%20but%20with%20a%20'Nation%20First'%20pledge%20to%20take%20the%20country%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20previous%20governments%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bchalta%20hai%26quot%3B%20--%20meaning%20lackadaisical%20--%20approach%20to%20reforms%20and%20development.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20environment%20of%20status%20quo.%20We%20had%20to%20break%20that%20mindset.%20The%20common%20man%20wanted%20change%2C%20but%20his%20dreams%20were%20not%20appreciated%20and%20he%20kept%20waiting%20for%20reforms.%20We%20implemented%20big%20reforms%2C%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20deprived%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20and%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20in%20his%20eleventh%20consecutive%20speech%20on%20the%20Independence%20Day%2C%20months%20after%20he%20started%20his%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723693800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fe0nbqpmo_pm-modi_625x300_15_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-nalanda-university-we-revived-nalanda-university-now-we-must-revive-nalanda-spirit-pm-modi-6341396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Addressing%20the%20nation%20on%20Independence%20Day%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20his%20government%20wants%20to%20develop%20an%20education%20system%20so%20that%20youngsters%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20abroad%20to%20study.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-nalanda-university-we-revived-nalanda-university-now-we-must-revive-nalanda-spirit-pm-modi-6341396%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B140%20Crore%20Indians%20Worried%20About%20Safety%20Of%20Hindus%20In%20Bangladesh%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20delivering%20his%2011th%20consecutive%20Independence%20Day%20speech%20at%20Delhi's%20Red%20Fort%2C%20said%20140%20crore%20Indians%20are%20worried%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20have%20faced%20attacks%20during%20the%20recent%20political%20unrest%20in%20the%20country%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B140%20crore%20Indian