a%20permanent%20shelter%20and%20cowshed%2C%20adjacent%20to%20his%20home.%20There%2C%20he%20found%20solace.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20pet%20cow%20with%20its%20small%20calf.%20I%20would%20play%20with%20the%20calf%20and%20they%20would%20come%20to%20me%20for%20pets.%20I%20was%20the%20most%20relaxed%20in%20their%20company%20as%20opposed%20to%20being%20around%20humans%20where%20I%20felt%20suffocated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHariom%20decided%20to%20follow%20his%20heart%E2%80%99s%20calling%20and%20ventured%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247423%2Fdairy-business-girl-buffalo-organic-earns-lakhs-nighoj-ahmednagar-maharashtra-inspiring-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edairy%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20a%20decision%20that%20initially%20drew%20scepticism%20and%20ridicule%20from%20the%20community.%20Starting%20with%20a%20modest%20investment%20of%20ten%20cows%2C%20he%20started%20selling%20milk%20to%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20not%20easy.%20Most%20of%20the%20cows%20were%20lactating%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20I%20would%20have%2050-60%20litres%20of%20surplus%20milk%20every%20day.%20Everybody%20had%20some%20regular%20milk%20sellers%2C%20so%20I%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20give%20away%20milk%20to%20people%20for%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20day%20started%20at%202am%20when%20he%20would%20milk%20the%20cows%20and%20move%20out%20in%20hope%20of%20making%20some%20sales.%20On%20a%20lucky%20day%2C%20he%20would%20make%20Rs%209%20profit%20while%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20milk%20was%20given%20away%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdhanya-dhenu-1723628100.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Despite%20ini