%20confidence%20among%20the%20women%2C%20who%20are%20now%20also%20making%20socks%20and%20caps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavani%2C%20a%20local%20artisan%20who%20previously%20had%20little%20success%20selling%20her%20artificial%20jewellery%2C%20saw%20200%20of%20her%20pieces%20sell%20out%20quickly%20after%20Amit%20encouraged%20her%20to%20display%20them%20at%20the%20caf%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20caf%C3%A9%20now%20features%20a%20dedicated%20counter%20displaying%20handcrafted%20items%20from%20local%20women%2C%20such%20as%20knitted%20mufflers%20and%20shawls.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-18.35.26_11zon-1723127605-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360420%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20now%20features%20a%20dedicated%20counter%20displaying%20handcrafted%20items%20from%20local%20