itive%20examination%2C%20minutes%20before%20the%20results%20were%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20confidence%20that%20I%20would%20clear%20the%20prelims.%20I%20was%20so%20unmotivated%20that%20I%20tried%20shifting%20my%20focus%20to%20the%20SSC-CGL%20exam.%20I%20was%20busy%20solving%20the%20previous%20year%20questions%20for%20it%20when%20my%20friend%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20had%20checked%20the%20results.%20I%20was%20so%20scared%20that%20I%20wondered%20how%20I%20would%20face%20my%20family%20and%20relatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20few%20more%20minutes%2C%20I%20somehow%20gathered%20courage%20and%20found%20my%20name%20on%20the%20list.%20I%20checked%20my%20roll%20number%20at%20least%2020%20times.%20The%20happiness%20of%20clearing%20the%20UPSC%20prelims%20gives%20a%20different%20level%20of%20satisfaction%20altogether%20than%20clearing%20all%20subsequent%20stages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20his%20worry%2C%20Vikas%20says%2C%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F235855%2Fupsc-topper-how-tips-method-irs-officer-failed-40-exams-inspiring-success-story-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHindi%20medium%20background%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20shatter%20the%20stereotypes%20by%20clearing%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%2C%20clenching%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20672.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20all%20set%20to%20undergo%20training%20as%20an%20Indian%20Foreign%20Officer%20(IFS)%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20IFS%20officer%20to%20understand%20the%20UPSC%20examination%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vikas%20celebrating%20with%20his%20friends%20after%20clearing%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-2-1723091324-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360266%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVikas%20celebrating%20with%20his%20friends%20after%20clearing%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMisconceptions%20and%20tips%20for%20Hindi-medium%20aspirants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20pursuing%20his%20B.Tech%20in%20a%20Delhi%20college%2C%20Vikas%20had%20decided%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20examination.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20came%20to%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20for%20a%20demo%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20hundreds%20of%20aspirants%20coming%20out%20of%20classes.%20I%20became%20hopeless%20seeing%20this%20crowd%20and%20wondered%20how%20I%20was%20going%20to%20survive%20here.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20small%20insect%20and%20feared%20losing%20my%20identity%20if%20I%20walked%20into%20that%20crowd%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20in%202021%2C%20he%20started%20preparing%20for%20the%20examination.%20He%20clears%20a%20few%20misconceptions%20and%20shares%20helpful%20tips%20for%20aspirants%20based%20on%20his%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Psychological%20barriers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20says%20that%20firstly%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20are%20told%20to%20join%20coaching%20institutes%20because%20without%20it%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20succeed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20psychological%20aspects%20which%20get%20affected%20due%20to%20senior%20culture%20in%20the%20lanes%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar.%20New%20candidates%20are%20expected%20to%20seek%20guidance%20from%20those%20who%20have%20already%20given%20multiple%20attempts.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebhaiyaji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Esirji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eculture.%20They%20put%20blind%20faith%20in%20them%20and%20consider%20those%20who%20cleared%20the%20exam%20as%20god%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecondly%2C%20most%20of%20these%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20come%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F238088%2Fips-hero-upsc-cse-examination-tips-strategy-free-online-webinar-suraj-singh-parihar-police-instagram-facebook-twitter-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20income%20backgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20immense%20financial%20stress%20on%20them.%20I%20have%20seen%20many%20of%20my%20other%20aspirant%20friends%20working%20in%20libraries%2C%20ATMs%2C%20and%20catering%20services.%20They%20would%20hide%20their%20face%20and%20step%20out%20for%20work%20in%20order%20to%20afford%20their%20fee.%20They%20never%20felt%20confident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vikas%20cleared%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%20in%20his%20second%20attempt.%5C%22%20srcset%3D