eejesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quarterfinal%20against%20Great%20Britain%20marked%20the%2023rd%20time%20Sreejesh%20stood%20in%20goal%20for%20India%20during%20a%20shoot-out%2C%20securing%20victory%20on%2013%20occasions.%20His%20performance%20was%20so%20extraordinary%20that%20a%20British%20coach%20watching%20from%20the%20stands%20exclaimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuperman!%E2%80%9D%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20abilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreejesh%20comes%20from%20a%20humble%20background%20in%20Kizhakkambalam%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Kochi%2C%20Kerala.%20Born%20into%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20he%20was%20fueled%20by%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sacrifice.%20Recognising%20his%20talent%2C%20his%20father%20had%20sold%20their%20cow%20to%20purchase%20a%20hockey%20kit%20for%20young%20Sreejesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20struggle%20had%20just%20begun%20for%20him.%20Sreejesh%20was%20constantly%20mocked%20for%20his%20looks%2C%20traditional%20attire%20(%3Cem%3Eveshti)%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Malayalam%20accent.%20Being%20told%20that%20a%20Kerala%20player%20would%20never%20make%20it%20big%20in%20Indian%20hockey%2C%20there%20were%20times%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20up.%20But%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20sacrifices%20kept%20him%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreejesh%20practised%20day%20and%20night%2C%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Indian%20junior%20hockey%20team.%20He%20won%20three%20Asian%20Games%20medals%2C%20including%20gold%20in%20Hangzhou%202022%2C%20which%20secured%20India%E2%80%99s%20spot%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359575%2Folympics-avinash-sable-india-paris-steeplechase-gold-medal-at-asian-games-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Named%20FIH%E2%80%99s%20(International%20Hockey%20Federation)%20best%20goalkeeper%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20he%20silenced%20his%20critics%20with%20his%20stellar%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hindustan%20Times%20article%20mentioned%20that%20Sreejesh%20believes%20a%20goalkeeper%20should%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98crazy%20person%E2%80%99%20and%20must%20know%20the%20art%20of%20intimidating.%20%E2%80%9CCrazy%2C%20because%20you%20just%20need%20to%20have%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20that%20ball.%20The%20second%20thing%20is%20aggression%3B%20you%20need%20to%20be%20an%20aggressive%20person%2C%20and%20those%20reflexes%20have%20to%20be%20there.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20much%20time%20to%20just%20think%2C%20%E2%80%98Save%E2%80%99.%20No%2C%20you%20just%20need%20to%20save%20it.%20Then%20you%20realise%2C%20%E2%80%98Okay%2C%20I%20made%20that%20save%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20acted%20as%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20lonely%20tusker%20is%20now%20representing%20India%20one%20last%20time%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20The%20country%20hopes%20for%20a%20medal%20as%20the%20ultimate%20farewell%20for%20its%20greatest%20goalkeeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20this%20video%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20PR%20Sreejesh%E2%80%99s%20journey%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQaJju-vhXek%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-